IQFEAT, UMI`\n  - `<sample>.libsum`: headerless four-column table (`sample, metric, value, pct`)\n\nUsing an output prefix `output/scrna_qc`, compute:\n  - `scrna_qc.libstats_reads.tsv`: per-library metrics (reads) as a wide table\n  - `scrna_qc.libstats_pct.tsv`: per-library metrics (percentages) as a wide table\nAnd render these per-plate PNGs (2 libraries per plate):\n  - `scrna_qc.reads_UMI_plot.png`\n  - `scrna_qc.plate_cUPM.png`\n  - `scrna_qc.plate_cRPM.png`\n  - `scrna_qc.plate_abs_transcripts.png`\nNormalize reads/UMI per cell by per-sample sum * 1e6 before the z-score heatmap.\n\n## Deliverables\n\n- At least `output/scrna_qc.reads_UMI_plot.png` must exist when you submit.\n- Full output set expected: scrna_qc.libstats_reads.tsv, scrna_qc.libstats_pct.tsv, scrna_qc.reads_UMI_plot.png, scrna_qc.plate_cUPM.png, scrna_qc.plate_cRPM.png, scrna_qc.plate_abs_transcripts.png under `output/`.\n\nWhen the deliverables are in `output/`, call `submit_done(success=true)` with a short\nsummary of how you solved it.\n\n## Workspace (read-only summary)\n```json\n{\n  \"OBJECTIVE.md\": {\n    \"_file\": \"OBJECTIVE.md\"\n  },\n  \"input\": {\n    \"qc\": {\n      \"cell_names.tsv\": {\n        \"_file\": \"cell_names.tsv\"\n      },\n      \"plate1_lib1.cellsum\": {\n        \"_file\": \"plate1_lib1.cellsum\"\n      },\n      \"plate1_lib1.libsum\": {\n        \"_file\": \"plate1_lib1.libsum\"\n      },\n      \"plate1_lib2.cellsum\": {\n        \"_file\": \"plate1_lib2.cellsum\"\n      },\n      \"plate1_lib2.libsum\": {\n        \"_file\": \"plate1_lib2.libsum\"\n      },\n      \"plate2_lib1.cellsum\": {\n        \"_file\": \"plate2_lib1.cellsum\"\n      },\n      \"plate2_lib1.libsum\": {\n        \"_file\": \"plate2_lib1.libsum\"\n      },\n      \"plate2_lib2.cellsum\": {\n        \"_file\": \"plate2_lib2.cellsum\"\n      },\n      \"plate2_lib2.libsum\": {\n        \"_file\": \"plate2_lib2.libsum\"\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"meta.json\": {\n    \"_file\": \"meta.json\"\n  },\n  \"output\": {}\n}\n```\n\nSuccess hint: when `output/scrna_qc.reads_UMI_plot.png` exists under the workspace, you may call submit_done(success=true).\n"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": null, "function_call": null, "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_BwHsVkLNgmj3iVo6FM0lBbfg", "type": "function", "function": {"arguments": "{\"plan\": \"1. Read the contents of the `input/qc/` directory to understand the structure and data within the `.cellsum` and `.libsum` files.\\n2. Process the `.libsum` files to create two wide tables: `scrna_qc.libstats_reads.tsv` and `scrna_qc.libstats_pct.tsv`.\\n3. Process the `.cellsum` files to normalize reads/UMI per cell by per-sample sum * 1e6.\\n4. Generate the required PNG plots:\\n   - `scrna_qc.reads_UMI_plot.png`\\n   - `scrna_qc.plate_cUPM.png`\\n   - `scrna_qc.plate_cRPM.png`\\n   - `scrna_qc.plate_abs_transcripts.png`\\n5. Save all outputs in the `output/` directory.\\n6. Verify the presence of `output/scrna_qc.reads_UMI_plot.png` and submit the task as complete.\"}", "name": "write_plan"}}]}, {"role": "tool", "content": "Wrote plan (658 chars) to .plan.md", "name": "write_plan", "tool_call_id": "call_BwHsVkLNgmj3iVo6FM0lBbfg"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": null, "function_call": null, "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_ILi5phhVlP7ICINxeDHW04GM", "type": "function", "function": {"arguments": "{}", "name": "list_workdir"}}]}, {"role": "tool", "content": "{\n  \"OBJECTIVE.md\": {\n    \"_file\": \"OBJECTIVE.md\"\n  },\n  \"input\": {\n    \"qc\": {\n      \"cell_names.tsv\": {\n        \"_file\": \"cell_names.tsv\"\n      },\n      \"plate1_lib1.cellsum\": {\n        \"_file\": \"plate1_lib1.cellsum\"\n      },\n      \"plate1_lib1.libsum\": {\n        \"_file\": \"plate1_lib1.libsum\"\n      },\n      \"plate1_lib2.cellsum\": {\n        \"_file\": \"plate1_lib2.cellsum\"\n      },\n      \"plate1_lib2.libsum\": {\n        \"_file\": \"plate1_lib2.libsum\"\n      },\n      \"plate2_lib1.cellsum\": {\n        \"_file\": \"plate